FRONTLINE ROADS v0.32.5 final audit

Behavior
- HP 0 combat facilities are detached immediately.
- HP 0 settlement buildings are removed immediately with their production queues.
- Destroyed gates leave no blocking barrier and enemy routes are recalculated.
- Placement nodes and edges become available immediately after destruction.
- Manual repair applies only to surviving damaged facilities.

Existing-save cleanup
- Legacy ruined or HP 0 combat facilities are removed during normalization.
- Legacy ruined, demolished, or HP 0 settlement buildings are removed during normalization.
- Orphan production queues are removed.
- Duplicate active defenses at the same node or edge are collapsed deterministically.
- Enemy targets pointing to removed facilities are cleared and rerouted.

Removed obsolete behavior
- Repairable wreck runtime states.
- Ruined gate and defense renderers.
- FIX and OPEN wreck markers.
- Wreck selection and wreck removal UI branches.
- Restored-tower restart delay.
- Offline loss calculations based on wreck counters.

Compatibility
- Save key unchanged: frontline_roads_refactor_v2
- Save schema unchanged: 2
